  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/aaf2397aa8fdc3283994b9991592187f.poster.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/aaf2397aa8fdc3283994b9991592187f.webm?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/aaf2397aa8fdc3283994b9991592187f.mp4?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>On an unhurried day, find a cozy spot, get comfortable, set the mood for wholesome, and open this unique interactive storybook.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/84b837c4f67de064e688fe02867f99ef.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=64 /></span><br>In Windreach, in a small apartment top floor, lived Finn and Gray, my favorite couple. Life is simple, perhaps a bit ordinary, and that is good. <br><br>Finn opens a sweets shop, and Gray is a truck driver. They don't have much, but luckily there is always food on the table. No matter what happens, they got each other.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/3da10c9f947baddea5fb19d3f3cea331.webp?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=49 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Made with Love</h2>A heartwarming experience inspired by personal life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/659df1c4924e027f7c7575e2b0449b6a.poster.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/659df1c4924e027f7c7575e2b0449b6a.webm?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/659df1c4924e027f7c7575e2b0449b6a.mp4?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sit Back and Relax</h2>There are no pressures, and you don't have to accomplish anything. Just like what life is supposed to be.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/0f80d8e97371693ba9e5042c87d5e5c5.poster.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/0f80d8e97371693ba9e5042c87d5e5c5.webm?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/0f80d8e97371693ba9e5042c87d5e5c5.mp4?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Light Comedy</h2>The story is fun and filled with joy. Perhaps a bit silly sometimes. Not too much, just enough to bring a smile to your face.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/4816c3d1f9d9973e0e6fbdb12d850841.poster.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/4816c3d1f9d9973e0e6fbdb12d850841.webm?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/4816c3d1f9d9973e0e6fbdb12d850841.mp4?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relentlessly Gay</h2>And I am proud of it! The next update will be even gayer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/eea48c79b597435f49f4bc7eacb64fc8.poster.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/eea48c79b597435f49f4bc7eacb64fc8.webm?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/eea48c79b597435f49f4bc7eacb64fc8.mp4?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bigger on the Inside</h2>What is it? Tap, drag, and press! It is a book you can both read and play.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/712fcf1731e3dd1a878331fd6db9d2be.poster.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/712fcf1731e3dd1a878331fd6db9d2be.webm?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/712fcf1731e3dd1a878331fd6db9d2be.mp4?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/8b8f94ce25c60c76202f64feffae577f.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/279fab4a96edeb13b07d8c9213784f19.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=128 /></span><br>On the occasion of my work being published, please allow me to introduce myself.<br><br>My name is Griffin Cyan, the author of this game. My avatar resembles me in real life.<br><br>The story of Omurice Next Time is deeply personal. The inspiration was drawn from my day-to-day life. I am more like Finn, and my boyfriend Garrett is basically Gray. It is a love letter, a memoir, and a vision.<br><br>There is always beauty in ordinary life. Love is long and lasting, kind of like mochi in soup.<br>To you, my dear readers, I sincerely hope you can find joy, peace, and strength in it.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/aaf2397aa8fdc3283994b9991592187f.poster.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/aaf2397aa8fdc3283994b9991592187f.webm?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/aaf2397aa8fdc3283994b9991592187f.mp4?t=1728974792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>On an unhurried day, find a cozy spot, get comfortable, set the mood for wholesome, and open this unique interactive storybook.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/84b837c4f67de064e688fe02867f99ef.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=64 /></span><br>In Windreach, in a small apartment top floor, lived Finn and Gray, my favorite couple. Life is simple, perhaps a bit ordinary, and that is good. <br><br>Finn opens a sweets shop, and Gray is a truck driver. They don't have much, but luckily there is always food on the table. No matter what happens, they got each other.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/3da10c9f947baddea5fb19d3f3cea331.webp?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=49 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Made with Love</h2>A heartwarming experience inspired by personal life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/659df1c4924e027f7c7575e2b0449b6a.poster.avif?t=1728974792\" width=618 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2670400/extras/659df1c492