om my day-to-day life. I am more like Finn, and my boyfriend Garrett is basically Gray. It is a love letter, a memoir, and a vision.<br><br>There is always beauty in ordinary life. Love is long and lasting, kind of like mochi in soup.<br>To you, my dear readers, I sincerely hope you can find joy, peace, and strength in it.",
